  "prompt": "What are the best institutes in Hyderabad for learning SAP Hana Cloud Integration Training?",
  "response": "As of the last update, several institutes in Hyderabad are known for providing quality SAP HANA Cloud Integration training. Here are some of the top ones:\n\n1. **Orien IT:**\n   - Provides a range of SAP courses including SAP HANA, SAP FICO, and SAP Cloud Integration.\n   - Practical and hands-on training.\n   - Experienced trainers.\n\n2. **Sapphire Global Consulting and Training:**\n   - Known for its comprehensive training programs in SAP.\n   - Offers real-time projects and case studies.\n\n3. **TekSlate:**\n   - Offers online training as well as classroom training.\n   - Known for its detailed course materials and interactive sessions.\n\n4. **Peopleclick Techno Solutions Pvt. Ltd.:**\n   - Focuses on practical and industry-oriented training.\n   - Experienced faculty members.\n\n5. **Igrow Technologies:**\n   - Provides intensive training programs in various SAP modules.\n   - Offers real-time scenarios and hands-on exercises.\n\n6. **Radiant Techlearning:**\n   - Provides both online and classroom training.\n   - Offers personalized training modules.\n\nIt is advisable to check the latest reviews, course content, trainer expertise, and training mode before enrolling in any institute. Direct interaction with the institutes can give you a better idea about their offerings and suitability for your needs.",
